high_descs: Go to the counter on your left, just ahead of you.
Pick up the knife in front of the fork, on the counter.
Turn to your left and go to the end of the counter, then turn to your right and go around to the other side of the counter, and turn towards the counter in front of the loaf of bread.
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave, past the refrigerator, on your right.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter where the sliced bread is.
Pick up one of the slices of bread off the counter.
Turn to your right and go back to the microwave, on your left, just past the refrigerator.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the slice of bred from the microwave.
Turn to your left and go past the sink, then turn to the counter on your right, where the toaster.
Place the slice of bread on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the microwave, and a slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left. go forward, turn left at the table

Go around the table to the opposite side of the table
Slice the bread on the table
Turn right, go to the counter, turn right to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn right and go to the table
Pick up a bread slice from the table
Turn right, go to the counter, turn right to the microwave
Put the bread slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the bread slice from the microwave
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the toaster
Put the bread on the counter
